For those who think the scout is heavily camped......not so.<br>
I do a lot of solo in WW, and have seen the scout up for hours on end.  Unfortunately, I tend to see her when the rest of Unhomed is either asleep or at work. A few days ago, I even tried to interest Fed in a go at the giant captain, but not near enough were interested.  I keep the scout turn-in  in my pack, and can trigger the giant spawn if we get enough in the zone.  After the fight we can random looting rights of the head.   Looter then gets the Benevolence item of their choice (melee bracer, int robe, or wis range slot)<br>
