ac17 str 8 sta 8, mr 12, Cr 12, Fr 5, hp 30, weight o.1<br>
<br>
Robe of Benevolence (Int casters) ac17, agi and dex neg 8, int 10, char 15, hp 25, mana 80<br>
<br>
Talisman of Benevolence (Wis casters) ac7, wis 15, Mr 12, Cr 12, Hp 38, mana 55 ...secondary or RANGE slot<br>
<br>
Beastlords can use both the bracer AND the Talisman.<br>
