<br>
The first is Plague of Insects this a Disease based slow for 25% and many mobs that have High MR are still vunerable to it. Combined with Insidious Decay that reduces the Disease resistance by 36 to 40 and most things can be slowed a little.<br>
<br>
For the Proper slow you need to have and Enchanter tash and a shammy malo or Mage Mala. these spells stack and all reduce MR and are all unresitable. Note that malo and mala are both 60th lvl spells. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/ffederationofpovarfrm3.showMessageRange?topicID=124.topic&start=21&stop=21>2</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub70.ezboard.com/ffederationofpovarfrm3.showPrevMessage?topicID=124.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub70.ezboard.com/ffederationofpovarfrm3.showNextMessage?topicID=124.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/ffederationofpovarfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=124.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/ffederationofpovarfrm3.emailToFriend?topicID=124.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/ffederationofpovarfrm3.threadControl?topicID=124.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/slate/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/ffederationofpovarfrm3.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=124.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/ffederationofpovarfrm3.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=124.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of repli